INSERT INTO `notice` VALUES (1,19,'为什么我家现在都不用毛巾了？',1,'aminds','xiugaiceshi@qq.com','毛巾','毛巾毛巾','https://news.suning.com/wtoutiao/witem2_2850732859.html',NULL,'<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">曾经有实验室做过测试：把新毛巾、用了3个月的毛巾、6个月以上的毛巾，分别进行细菌培育。实验发现，以每平方公分核算，新毛巾菌数量，基本在100这个量级上；3个月的毛巾菌落，在1万量级上；而用了6个月以上的毛巾，培育皿上几乎长满了菌落，预估超百万量级。所以说呢，大部分时候，你的毛巾仅仅是“看上去很干净”而已……</p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181003/1538537146397735.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">不过，就算看到如此悲壮的实验结果，但你也不用太紧张！毕竟，虽然我们不能阻止细菌的繁殖，但我们可以选择放弃毛巾！在这里，小编建议，使用“日抛型”的毛巾替代品——棉柔巾：一次一张，可以有效远离细菌的滋生！更何况，这款网红爆品还可以干湿两用呢！</p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181003/1538537147266082.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">水流下，大家尽管放心搓洗——反正该怎么洗毛巾就怎么搓它！全新维达棉柔巾，采用精选棉花配合密纹交织工艺，棉柔巾哪怕用水多次冲洗或者双手反复揉搓，它依然强韧如初，不起棉不掉絮，一点都不用担心它会洗着洗着就散了……</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">是什么让它这么优秀？！初试第一触，你指尖上的肌肤便已知道，我们这次的新品确实是下了苦工啊！从源头开始，甚至每一朵棉花都经过了严格的挑选方可入围，成为我们精选的优质原材料。然后，经过一道又一道的密纹交织工艺，一关又一关的安全检测，最终那些表现得特别好的，我们才小心翼翼地把它放进包装，送到你的面前。</p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181003/1538537148161285.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">有颜又有料，技多不压身。我家棉柔巾啊，除了经得起洗刷刷的考验，在清洁力这道考验面前也是表现出色的。一般的污迹啊，唇印啊，用它轻轻一擦，搞定！嗯，就是这么魔性~~</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">拒绝给细菌提供滋生的温床，值得你一囤再囤的好宝贝——维达棉柔巾，从宝宝护理到洁面护肤，细心呵护你和家人每一寸的娇嫩肌肤。身边的妈妈们早就入手，说给孩子做御用的肌肤清洁巾了！你真的应该试一试！</p><p><br/></p>',1538537150,0),(2,28,'婚宴喝什么酒好？婚宴用酒推荐',1,'admins','771660658@qq.com','婚宴用酒 1','婚宴用酒推荐','https://news.suning.com/wtoutiao/witem2_2745677168.html',NULL,'<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">结婚最重要的一个环节就是婚宴了，在婚宴上，婚宴酒又是不可缺少的一部分。一般的婚宴上用的都是白酒、洋酒、红酒和啤酒。中国自古有无酒不成席的说法，所以婚宴用酒当然得要好好的挑选一下。在中国白酒的品牌也多种多样，那么哪些白酒适合婚宴用酒呢？接下来就给大家推荐一番啦！</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong>茅台酒</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">尊为中国国酒，以独特的色、香、味为世人称颂。一般52~54度，产于贵州省仁还县茅台镇，因产地而得名。该厂位于赤水河畔，有270余年的历史。茅台酒具有“酱香突出，幽雅细腻，酒体醇厚，回味悠长”的特殊风格，酒液清亮，醇香馥郁，香而不艳，低而不淡，闻之沁人心脾，入口荡气回肠，饮后余香绵绵。茅台酒最大的特点是“空杯留香好”，即酒尽杯空后，酒杯内仍余香绵绵，经久不散。茅台酒在历次国家名酒评选中，都荣获名酒称号。茅台酒还是许多重大的外事活动的见证人，因而被誉：“国酒”，“外交酒”。</p><p><a class=\"good-wrapper lazy-dom\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://product.suning.com/0000000000/000000000191006629.html?srcPoint=2745677168&src=2745677168\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; display: block; width: 435px; height: 110px; margin: 10px 0px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></a></p><p><br/></p><p><img alt=\"贵州茅台 王子酒 53度500ml*6 整箱装 酱香型白酒\" class=\"lazy-loading\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181003/1538537296510742.jpg\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"/></p><p class=\"good-name\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16px; font-size: 14px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; height: 32px; font-weight: bold; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical;\">贵州茅台 王子酒 53度500ml*6 整箱装 酱香型白酒</p><p><span class=\"price\"><em style=\"font-style: normal;\">¥</em>&nbsp;<em style=\"font-style: normal; margin-right: 10px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 24px; line-height: 28px;\">948.00</em>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-decoration:line-through;\"><em style=\"font-style: normal;\">¥</em>&nbsp;<em style=\"font-style: normal;\">948.00</em></span></p><p class=\"buy\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; font-size: 14px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; position: absolute; right: 10px; bottom: 5px; height: 32px; width: 80px; border-radius: 4px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background: rgb(235, 56, 15); text-align: center;\">去购买</p><p class=\"buy\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; font-size: 14px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; position: absolute; right: 10px; bottom: 5px; height: 32px; width: 80px; border-radius: 4px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background: rgb(235, 56, 15); text-align: center;\"><a class=\"good-wrapper lazy-dom\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://product.suning.com/0000000000/000000000191006629.html?srcPoint=2745677168&src=2745677168\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; display: block; width: 435px; height: 110px; margin: 10px 0px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></a></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong>剑南春</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">绵竹剑南春酒，产于四川省绵竹市，因绵竹在清代属剑南道，故称“剑南春”。四川的绵竹市素有“酒乡”之称，绵竹市因产竹产酒而得名。早在唐代就产闻名遐迩的名酒——“剑南烧春”，相传李白为喝此美酒曾在这里况把皮袄卖掉买酒痛饮，留下“士解金貂”、“解貂赎酒”的佳话。北宋苏轼称赞这种蜜酒“三日开瓮香满域”，“甘露微浊醍醐清”，其酒之引人可见一斑。</p><p><a class=\"good-wrapper lazy-dom\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://product.suning.com/0000000000/000000000140220226.html?srcPoint=2745677168&src=2745677168\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; display: block; width: 435px; height: 110px; margin: 10px 0px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; backgro