text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">在右边的调台旋钮上，采用了金属的旋钮设计，手感模仿怀旧复古的收音机调台机械旋钮，再配搭真皮的装饰搭配，尽显倍加复古优雅感觉。收音机开启后，调台旋钮内有着LED背光灯设计，具有怀旧复古般钨丝灯光背景灯色，怀旧复古做到了极致。</p><p><img src=\"https://image4.suning.cn/uimg/MFS/show/153822503425620283.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">另外两个旋钮，分别是音量与功能旋钮，与调台旋钮一样采用金属设计，同时也附加上真皮装饰设计。两旋钮采用了新式步进多功能电位器设计，而且遵循怀旧复古的感觉，把操作起来的手感模仿传统老式机械电位器的手感。其中，在音量旋钮中，除了能旋转，还加入了按压开关，能实现播放的暂停与开始。</p><p><img src=\"https://image5.suning.cn/uimg/MFS/show/153822503440239383.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">猫王旅行者2号后面按一贯现代产品惯例，把产品的铭牌信息统一清晰标注。其中WiFi配网键、USB/AUXIN（可用于充电）接口、配有定位孔的复古AI麦克风输入接口、复位孔都位于收音机中间部位，方便进行操作与连接。</p><p><img src=\"https://image3.suning.cn/uimg/MFS/show/153822503450801562.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">其中，为了实现强劲、震撼的低频效果，巧妙地透过全频喇叭，配搭低频振膜与独特的低频气动气道设计，预留出重低音低频排气孔。在100%满载音量，播放蔡琴《渡口》，在排气口能给你带来阵风般的震撼吹风体验。只要在排气孔处贴一张薄纸，会吹出与垂直面将近90°的直角效果，低频效果动力之大，让惊叹不已。</p><p><img src=\"https://image3.suning.cn/uimg/MFS/show/153822503478067605.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">猫王旅行者2号拥有425g的重量，再配搭具有强劲的输出震撼力。由于，整体与桌面的震动，会产生各种同频共振的问题，造成共振噪音干扰，影响内部结构的稳定，从而影响音质播放效果。为了避免上诉情况出现，猫王旅行者2号不得不采用了4个具有吸音防震的橡胶材质的垫脚，完美实现减震静音的效果，提升稳定，保证Hi-Fi级震撼的音质输出，给你带来意想不到的效果。</p><p><img src=\"https://image5.suning.cn/uimg/MFS/show/153822503493960444.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">猫王旅行者2号这次保留了蓝牙输入与有线输入，但取消了传统的FM功能，大胆地加入了更加丰富多彩、不受地区局限性的网络电台，更把调频旋钮更改为调台旋钮，一共有12个频道，而且用罗马数字标注。而且配搭有专属APP——Oh Play（猫王妙播），配合其选台等其他功能操控。</p><p><img src=\"https://image2.suning.cn/uimg/MFS/show/153822503510042168.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">在Oh Play（猫王妙播）APP的引导界面中，说明了为何猫王要做怀旧复古收音机的原因，也体验了&#39;中国胆机之父&#39;曾德钧先生对收音机热爱之情怀。猫王旅行者2号作为一款附有时代色彩，复古未来风怀旧产品。它不仅拥有复古情怀与功能，结合了科技美学典范，打造出具有AI智能的互联网产品，正是猫王的定位与追求的潮人桌面BGM神器。</p><p><img src=\"https://image5.suning.cn/uimg/MFS/show/153822503523067411.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Oh Play（猫王妙播）需要注册登录使用，根据你的喜爱需要，为你进行个性化的私人定制，你就可以选取你爱听的音乐，AI智能为你提供 精选的BGM音乐，好听到停不下来。</p><p><img src=\"https://image2.suning.cn/uimg/MFS/show/153822503538917264.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">打开收音机，根据导向提示链接匹配WiFi网络，等待匹配连接完成，就可以开启猫王收音机不受地域限制、拥有丰富多彩资源的网络FM收听了。APP就会根据你选择的爱好分类，智能为你定制专属的电台频道，再配搭猫王悉心调校的音质，让你陶醉在音乐之中。</p><p><img src=\"https://image3.suning.cn/uimg/MFS/show/153822503549554536.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span><img src=\"https://image3.suning.cn/uimg/MFS/show/153822503566332224.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">而且在自定义频道中，包括FM、博客、音乐三大分类，每个分类中更有各种不同风格的种类给你自定义选择。在AI的加持下，APP会选择最适合你的频道进行音乐播放。猫王旅行者2号秉承猫王&#39;灵魂曲线&#39;的声音调教，把带有胆机音色的动听的音乐，给耳朵更舒适的声音陪伴。</p><p><img src=\"https://image2.suning.cn/uimg/MFS/show/153822503581554823.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-v