xt-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\">标题对于一篇文章的重要性不言而喻。标题分为两个部分，一个是标题的主题，即标题说了什么，一个是标题的形式/技巧，即标题是怎么说的。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\">其实，能妹私以为，标题的主题是比标题技巧要更重要的，有的话题天生自带热点，爆起来毫不费力，所以在构思一篇文章之前，先要做好选题，在此基础上，我们再来个1、2、3的步骤写标题。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\">首先确定好主题，写完内容，标题可以先随便起</span></p><p style=\"margin: 22px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; font-family: arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span class=\"bjh-p\">写完内容后，罗列文章所有亮点，比如名人（谁谁用过，谁穿过，谁夸过）、价格（直接写，跟大牌对比、平价之光等）、逆天的