INSERT INTO `notice` VALUES (11,28,'秋冬季节想吃就吃！自制火锅养生不养膘',1,'hhyytt','881665822@qq.com',NULL,NULL,'https://news.suning.com/wtoutiao/witem2_7671632118.html','2018-10-08/bf24966f3b1947b1627dd4ce7f937890.jpg','<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">连日来的连续降温，干燥阴冷的秋冬天这就来了。此时身为敬业小编的我，不由的想起了一句歌词“行走在冬夜的冷风中 飘散的 踩碎的 都是梦 孤单单这一刻......”秋冬最不可缺少的就是火锅啦！作为冬日里的必备饮食。火锅真是既暖胃又养生的家常经典啊，既滋补又驱寒、加入不同的食材，营养价值、功效都大有不同哦。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">下面让虫子小编领着您看看秋冬常吃的四种火锅分别是哪些吧！</p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181008/1539000405283752.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">一、牛肉火锅</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">1. 牛肉富含蛋白质，氨基酸组成比猪肉更接近人体需要，能提高机体抗病能力，秋冬季节天气寒冷，吃一顿热腾腾的牛肉火锅，既滋补又美味；</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">2. 牛肉有补中益气，滋养脾胃，强健筋骨，化痰息风，止渴止涎之功效，适宜于中气下隐、气短体虚之人食用；</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">3. 水牛肉能安胎补神，黄牛肉能安中益气、健脾养胃、强筋壮骨。</p><p><a class=\"good-wrapper lazy-dom\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://product.suning.com/0070165068/000000010010029545.html?srcPoint=7671632118&src=7671632118\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; display: block; width: 435px; height: 110px; margin: 10px 0px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></a></p><p><img alt=\"嘉食和 阿根廷 小公牛 牛腱肉共1.5kg 高品质牛腱 浓浓牛肉香 牛腿肉非牛排 生鲜牛肉 顺丰发货\" class=\"lazy-loading\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181008/1539000406625976.jpg\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"/></p><p class=\"good-name\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 16px; font-size: 14px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; height: 32px; font-weight: bold; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical;\">嘉食和 阿根廷 小公牛 牛腱肉共1.5kg 高品质牛腱 浓浓牛肉香 牛腿肉非牛排 生鲜牛肉 顺丰发货</p><p><span class=\"price\"><em style=\"font-style: normal;\">¥</em>&nbsp;<em style=\"font-style: normal; margin-right: 10px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 24px; line-height: 28px;\">176.00</em>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-decoration:line-through;\"><em style=\"font-style: normal;\">¥</em>&nbsp;<em style=\"font-style: normal;\">176.00</em></span></p><p class=\"buy\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; font-size: 14px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; position: absolute; right: 10px; bottom: 5px; height: 32px; width: 80px; border-radius: 4px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background: rgb(235, 56, 15); text-align: center;\">去购买</p><p><a class=\"good-wrapper lazy-dom\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://product.suning.com/0070165068/000000010010029545.html?srcPoint=7671632118&src=7671632118\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none; outline: 0px; cursor: pointer; display: block; width: 435px; height: 110px; margin: 10px 0px; padding-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p class=\"buy\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 32px; font-size: 14px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; position: absolute; right: 10px; bottom: 5px; height: 32px; width: 80px; border-radius: 4px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background: rgb(235, 56, 15); text-align: center;\"><br/></p></a></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">原料：牛腱1100g、白萝卜、八角、干红椒、桂皮、蒜瓣、红油火锅底料、老抽、菠菜、生姜。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">做法：</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">1.牛肉洗净、切块。切好的牛肉放入盆中，加入冷水浸泡出血水，多换几次水，至水清。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">2.准备好八角、桂皮、干红椒、生姜、蒜瓣。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">3.牛肉倒入高压锅，加入适量冷水，大火煮开，撇净血沫；倒入八角、桂皮等辅料，加入盐、老抽。大火煮开后，小火炖40分钟。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">4.牛肉煮软，下入白萝卜，再将煮好的牛肉转入火锅中，倒入菠菜，边煮边吃。</p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181008/1539000407403259.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &qu