<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">1.猪蹄中的胶原蛋白质在烹调过程中可转化成明胶，从而有效改善机体生理功能和皮肤组织细胞的储水功能，防止皮肤过早褶皱，延缓皮肤衰老；</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">2.猪蹄对于经常四肢疲乏，腿部抽筋、麻木，消化道出血；</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">3.猪蹄含丰富的胶原蛋白，可促进毛皮生长，预治进行性肌营养不良症，使冠心病和脑血管病得到改善。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">原料：猪蹄500g、干辣椒、花椒、香菜、花椒油、十三香、土豆、白菜、粉条、豆腐、豆瓣酱。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">做法：</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">1.猪蹄剁成块儿焯水备用。锅中下油，油烧热后下姜蒜和干辣椒、花椒炒出香味，下入猪蹄同炒。加入十三香、盐、油辣椒继续翻炒。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">2.将猪蹄转入压力锅，加适量的清水，压半小时。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">4.土豆切块，下炒锅煸香，加入盐、豆瓣酱翻炒均匀。将翻炒后的土豆和白菜、豆腐、粉条等一同放入火锅中。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">5.将炖好的猪蹄放在蔬菜上面，滴入少许花椒油，开火边吃边煮。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">是不是特别想吃呢？吃火锅的应该按照先荤后素的顺序，要注意的是—烫食时汤汁一定要滚开，要全部浸入汤汁中烫食；其次是调节麻辣味，方法是：喜麻辣着，可从火锅边上油处烫食；反之则从中间沸腾处烫食；再次就是吃火锅时，必须配一杯茶，以开胃消食，解油去腻，换换口味，减轻麻辣之感。而想充分的把上面这些美味和营养都激发出来的话，就需要一个专业的电磁炉来做料理！</p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181008/1539000410191101.jpg\" class=\"bigPic\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">品质生活静享烹饪；好炉识火，煲汤入味；一个好的电磁炉，最重要